00:39:52,579 --> 00:39:56,124
Tunggu. Sebentar.

502
00:39:56,375 --> 00:39:58,627
Tutup!

503
00:39:58,710 --> 00:39:59,920
Satu pukulan lagi.

504
00:40:10,138 --> 00:40:12,641
Senter besar ini tak berguna.

505
00:40:16,228 --> 00:40:19,773
Daripada bermain seharian,
ganti baterai saja.

506
00:40:37,374 --> 00:40:38,834
Kau tak beli ini?

507
00:40:43,797 --> 00:40:45,966
Mungkin dijatuhkan para bajingan Busan itu

508
00:40:46,049 --> 00:40:47,884
saat mereka menyerang waktu itu.

509
00:40:48,885 --> 00:40:51,805
Maksudmu mereka polisi?

510
00:40:51,888 --> 00:40:53,056
Kenapa polisi melakukan itu?

511
00:40:54,933 --> 00:40:56,268
Aku tak tahu.

512
00:40:58,520 --> 00:41:00,355
Jadi, polisi menyamar jadi preman

513
00:41:00,439 --> 00:41:02,274
dan menghancurkan kantor kita?

514
00:41:03,650 --> 00:41:04,735
Kenapa?

515
00:41:12,784 --> 00:41:13,910
Permisi.

516
00:41:16,538 --> 00:41:17,914
Hei, ada apa?

517
