Ya.

518
00:41:21,626 --> 00:41:22,878
Baik, tunggu di situ.

519
00:41:31,303 --> 00:41:32,303
Smith.

520
00:41:32,387 --> 00:41:33,722
Ya, Manajer Cho?

521
00:41:33,805 --> 00:41:35,182
Menurutmu dia datang sendiri?

522
00:41:35,974 --> 00:41:37,017
Tampaknya begitu.

523
