Ayo. Cepat.

527
00:41:57,162 --> 00:41:58,413
Bodoh.

528
00:42:06,004 --> 00:42:07,214
Arlojimu bagus.

529
00:42:08,548 --> 00:42:09,549
Benar.

530
00:42:10,384 --> 00:42:11,593
Kau datang sendiri?

531
00:42:11,676 --> 00:42:12,761
Ya, Pak.

532
00:42:14,346 --> 00:42:15,347
Baby.

533
00:42:16,556 --> 00:42:18,016
Hei, lenganmu.

534
00:42:18,767 --> 00:42:20,268
Coba lihat...

535
00:42:24,022 --> 00:42:25,524
Tunggu.

536
00:42:25,607 --> 00:42:26,607
Biar aku...

537
00:42:32,614 --> 00:42:35,534
Jangan bicara di sini,
ayo kita ke tempat pribadi.

538
00:42:40,497 --> 00:42:41,998
Maaf.

539
00:43:02,561 --> 00:43:05,105
Kami tak bisa meninggalkan mayat
di sekolah dasar.

540
00:43:06,690 --> 00:43:08,442
Nanti anak-anak takut.

541
00:43:09,401 --> 00:43:10,402
Benar?

542
00:43:11,695 --> 00:43:12,904
Benar, Pak.

543
00:43:22,956 --> 00:43:23,957
Giring dia.

544
00:43:36,553 --> 00:43:38,263
Arlojinya bagus sekali.

545
00:43:38,346 --> 00:43:40,432
Aku iri sekali!

546
00:43:44,770 --> 00:43:46,063
Sial.

547
00:43:47,230 --> 00:43:49,566
Ini, coba pakai arlojinya.

548
00:43:50,484 --> 00:43:51,484
Bagaimana?

549
00:43:54,613 --> 00:43:55,614
Apa-apaan?

550
00:43:55,739 --> 00:43:56,865
Dia mau apa?

551
00:43:57,407 --> 00:43:58,909
Manajer Cho.

552
00:43:58,992 --> 00:44:01,870
Hei! Apa-apaan kau?

553
00:44:07,042 --> 00:44:09,544
Apa-apaan ini?

554
00:44:10,170 --> 00:44:11,963
Baby, periksalah.

555
00:44:14,424 --> 00:44:16,218
Leherku sakit.

556
00:44:16,968 --> 00:44:18,095
Sial!

557
00:44:26,353 --> 00:44:27,521
Hei, Nona!

558
00:44:27,938 --> 00:44:31,733
Keluar dari mobil! Leherku sakit sekali!

559
00:44:31,817 --> 00:44:32,901
Nona!

560
00:44:34,528 --> 00:44:35,737
Apa?

561
00:44:39,491 --> 00:44:40,659
Apa-apaan?

562
00:44:41,243 --> 00:44:42,786
Hei! Silau!

563
00:44:45,288 --> 00:44:46,373
Sial!

564
00:44:47,290 --> 00:44:49,418
Kau...

565
00:45:18,030 --> 00:45:19,197
Kwon Seungho.

566
00:45:19,281 --> 00:45:20,449
Ya?

567
00:45:21,158 --> 00:45:22,159
Hei.

568
00:45:23,869 --> 00:45:24,869
Ikut aku.

569
00:45:27,039 --> 00:45:28,040
Ayo.

570
00:45:58,111 --> 00:45:59,321
Hei.

571
00:45:59,404 --> 00:46:03,450
Siapa bilang kau boleh pakai
celana dalam mewah begini, Bajingan?

572
00:46:04,284 --> 00:46:05,619
Dasar sampah.

573
00:46:06,870 --> 00:46:07,996
Hei.

574
00:46:09,206 --> 00:46:10,374
Bajingan.

575
00:46:10,832 --> 00:46:12,167
Ayo.

576
00:46:12,250 --> 00:46:13,752
Jawab aku.

577
00:46:13,835 --> 00:46:14,836
Siapa itu?

578
00:46:15,921 --> 00:46:17,172
Hai.

579
00:46:19,299 --> 00:46:21,009
Dia berengsek.

580
00:46:21,093 --> 00:46:22,511
Dia coba membunuh Bos

581
00:46:22,594 --> 00:46:23,720
dan merusak bisnis kita.

582
00:46:23,804 --> 00:46:25,305
Mau kita apakan dia?

583
00:46:27,933 --> 00:46:28,934
Bunuh dia.

584
00:46:29,226 --> 00:46:30,685
Benar? Kau juga sependapat?

585
00:46:32,396 --> 00:46:33,980
Bajingan.

586
00:46:37,651 --> 00:46:38,652
Bukan kau?

587
00:46:39,736 --> 00:46:41,113
Lalu kenapa kita melakukan ini?

588
00:46:41,947 --> 00:46:43,824
Pikirmu omong kosong ini tanpa alasan?

589
00:46:44,616 --> 00:46:46,451
- Tidak?
- Berhenti gemetar, Jalang.

590
00:46:47,911 --> 00:46:49,579
Bajingan.

591
00:46:49,663 --> 00:46:50,956
Mendongak.

592
00:46:51,039 --> 00:46:52,916
Bajingan.

593
00:46:55,001 --> 00:46:56,002
Tegakkan dia.

594
00:46:59,423 --> 00:47:00,465
Hei.

595
00:47:00,549 --> 00:47:01,383
Ayo.

596
00:47:01,466 --> 00:47:03,260
Angkat tanganmu.

597
00:47:03,343 --> 00:47:04,428
Pegang erat-erat.

598
00:47:04,511 --> 00:47:05,721
Satu, dua, tiga.

599
00:47:08,098 --> 00:47:10,517
Pikirmu itu akan membunuhnya?

600
00:47:10,600 --> 00:47:11,893
Kau saja yang lakukan.

601
00:47:11,977 --> 00:47:13,270
Apa kau suka dia?

602
00:47:13,603 --> 00:47:15,147
Lakukanlah, Bajingan.

603
00:47:16,857 --> 00:47:17,941
Angkat dia.

604
00:47:19,609 --> 00:47:21,153
Akan kupukul di sini.

605
00:47:21,653 --> 00:47:22,653
Di sini.

606
00:47:26,116 --> 00:47:27,701
Dasar jalang.

607
00:47:31,621 --> 00:47:32,621
Berengsek.

608
00:47:33,749 --> 00:47:34,875
Jangan tegang, Jalang.

609
00:47:39,296 --> 00:47:42,090
Jalang ini layak dipukul
untuk celana dalam bagusnya.

610
00:47:42,174 --> 00:47:43,175
Kemari.

611
00:47:45,552 --> 00:47:46,636
Waktunya dipukul.

612
00:47:48,221 --> 00:47:49,264
Satu.

613
00:47:50,557 --> 00:47:51,558
Dua.

614
00:47:53,518 --> 00:47:55,354
Sekali lagi.

615
00:47:55,437 --> 00:47:57,981
- Tiga.
- Cukup. Berhenti.

616
00:48:00,442 --> 00:48:02,110
Cukup main-mainnya. Selesaikan.

617
00:48:03,653 --> 00:48:04,654
Ya, Bos.

